AGI - "On the occasion of the 208 anniversary of the constitution of the Body, I am pleased to express gratitude and appreciation to the women and men of the Police for the constant and generous commitment to the service of the State. The Penitentiary Police are called daily to face difficult situations of tension and suffering, increasingly frequent due to the serious phenomenon of overcrowding > in place". The President of the Republic Sergio Mattarella says so.
"The high professionalism and the spirit of service of the members of the Body make a decisive contribution to the implementation of the constitutional principle of the educational function of the penalty for the possible reintegration into the social life of the prisoners, despite the very critical conditions of the prison system.
<div </div
On this day, I renew on behalf of the Republic felt expressions of gratitude > and of support to the staff of the Penitentiary Police and, at the same time, I address a moving thought to those who have lost their lives or have been injured in fulfilling their duty," concludes Mattarella.&nbsp;
&nbsp;

